{
  "video_id": "okpg-lVWLbE",
  "title": "6 Problems with our School System",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 357.0,
      "end_time": 1822.0,
      "text": "There is a growing feeling today"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 1822.0,
      "end_time": 4699.0,
      "text": "that something is wrong with our system of education."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 4699.0,
      "end_time": 6240.0,
      "text": "But what is it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 6240.0,
      "end_time": 8189.0,
      "text": "Well, we send our children to school"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 8189.0,
      "end_time": 9924.0,
      "text": "to prepare them for the real world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 9924.0,
      "end_time": 12811.0,
      "text": "which is changing very, very fast."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 12811.0,
      "end_time": 16727.0,
      "text": "But our schools haven't changed much for hundreds of years."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 16758.0,
      "end_time": 19793.0,
      "text": "In fact, thought leaders from around the world agree"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 19793.0,
      "end_time": 21471.0,
      "text": "that the current system of education"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 21472.0,
      "end_time": 23452.0,
      "text": "was designed in the Industrial Age,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 23452.0,
      "end_time": 25890.0,
      "text": "mainly to churn out factory workers."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 25890.0,
      "end_time": 30421.0,
      "text": "And this Industrial Age mentality of mass production and mass control"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 30455.0,
      "end_time": 33498.0,
      "text": "still runs deep in schools."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 33498.0,
      "end_time": 35330.0,
      "text": "Industrial Age values."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 36657.0,
      "end_time": 38699.0,
      "text": "We educate children by batches,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 38699.0,
      "end_time": 41562.0,
      "text": "and govern their lives by ringing bells."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 41562.0,
      "end_time": 45119.0,
      "text": "All day long, students do nothing but follow instructions."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 45119.0,
      "end_time": 49272.0,
      "text": "Sit down, take out your books, turn to page 40,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 49272.0,
      "end_time": 52696.0,
      "text": "solve problem number three, stop talking."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 52696.0,
      "end_time": 56885.0,
      "text": "At school, you're rewarded for doing exactly what you're told."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 56900.0,
      "end_time": 61372.0,
      "text": "These are Industrial Age values that were really important for factory workers."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 61447.0,
      "end_time": 63891.0,
      "text": "Their success depended on following instructions"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 63891.0,
      "end_time": 66859.0,
      "text": "and doing exactly what they were told."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 66859.0,
      "end_time": 71645.0,
      "text": "But in today's world, how far can you get by simply following instructions?"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 71723.0,
      "end_time": 74317.0,
      "text": "The modern world values people who can be creative,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 74317.0,
      "end_time": 76232.0,
      "text": "who can communicate their ideas,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 76232.0,
      "end_time": 78642.0,
      "text": "and collaborate with others."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 78642.0,
      "end_time": 80101.0,
      "text": "But our children don't get a chance"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 80101.0,
      "end_time": 82568.0,
      "text": "to develop such skills in a system that's based"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 82568.0,
      "end_time": 84651.0,
      "text": "on Industrial Age values."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 85769.0,
      "end_time": 88186.0,
      "text": "Lack of autonomy and control."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 89139.0,
      "end_time": 93565.0,
      "text": "At school, our children experience a complete lack of autonomy and control."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 93619.0,
      "end_time": 94972.0,
      "text": "Every minute of a child's life"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 94972.0,
      "end_time": 97702.0,
      "text": "is tightly controlled by the system."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 97702.0,
      "end_time": 100319.0,
      "text": "But in today's world, if you're doing important work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 100319.0,
      "end_time": 102223.0,
      "text": "then you're managing your own time."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 102223.0,
      "end_time": 103572.0,
      "text": "You're making your own decisions"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 103572.0,
      "end_time": 107633.0,
      "text": "regarding what to do and when to do it."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 107633.0,
      "end_time": 110211.0,
      "text": "But life at school looks very different."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 110212.0,
      "end_time": 113881.0,
      "text": "The system is sending a dangerous message to our children,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 113881.0,
      "end_time": 116576.0,
      "text": "that they are not in charge of their own lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 116576.0,
      "end_time": 118707.0,
      "text": "They just have to follow whatever is laid down,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 118707.0,
      "end_time": 122619.0,
      "text": "instead of taking charge and making the most of their lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 122620.0,
      "end_time": 124340.0,
      "text": "Experts believe autonomy"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 124340.0,
      "end_time": 126805.0,
      "text": "is incredibly important for children."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 126805.0,
      "end_time": 128732.0,
      "text": "It's no wonder then that our children"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 128732.0,
      "end_time": 131994.0,
      "text": "are bored and demotivated by school."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 131994.0,
      "end_time": 134967.0,
      "text": "Can you imagine how you would feel if you were told exactly what to do"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 134968.0,
      "end_time": 137468.0,
      "text": "for every minute of your life?"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 138309.0,
      "end_time": 140827.0,
      "text": "Inauthentic learning."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 140827.0,
      "end_time": 144310.0,
      "text": "Most of the learning that happens in schools today is not authentic,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 144510.0,
      "end_time": 148160.0,
      "text": "because it relies on memorization and rote learning."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 148234.0,
      "end_time": 152409.0,
      "text": "The system defines a generic set of knowledge that all children must know."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 152480.0,
      "end_time": 158452.0,
      "text": "And then, every few months, we measure how much has been retained by administering exams."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 158505.0,
      "end_time": 161170.0,
      "text": "We know that such learning is not authentic"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 161170.0,
      "end_time": 164785.0,
      "text": "because most of it is gone the day after the exam."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 164785.0,
      "end_time": 168286.0,
      "text": "Learning can be much deeper and more authentic."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 168286.0,
      "end_time": 172539.0,
      "text": "It can be so much more than just memorization and retention."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 172539.0,
      "end_time": 174290.0,
      "text": "But that's the only thing we measure,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 174290.0,
      "end_time": 177438.0,
      "text": "and test scores are the only thing we value."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 177438.0,
      "end_time": 182896.0,
      "text": "This has created an extremely unhealthy culture for students, parents, and teachers."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 182969.0,
      "end_time": 185249.0,
      "text": "Children are going through endless hours of tuitions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 185249.0,
      "end_time": 190777.0,
      "text": "staying up all night memorizing useless facts that they will forget very soon."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 190833.0,
      "end_time": 194288.0,
      "text": "No room for passions and interests."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 194288.0,
      "end_time": 196563.0,
      "text": "We have an extremely standardized system,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 196563.0,
      "end_time": 202017.0,
      "text": "where each child must learn the same thing at the same time in the same way as everyone else."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 202100.0,
      "end_time": 205160.0,
      "text": "This doesn't respect the basic fact of being human,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 205160.0,
      "end_time": 208460.0,
      "text": "that each of us is unique and different in our own way."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 208461.0,
      "end_time": 211718.0,
      "text": "We all have different passions and interests."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 211718.0,
      "end_time": 213298.0,
      "text": "And the key to fulfilment in life"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 213299.0,
      "end_time": 215704.0,
      "text": "is to find your passion."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 215704.0,
      "end_time": 218308.0,
      "text": "But do the schools of today help our children"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 218308.0,
      "end_time": 221552.0,
      "text": "find and develop their passion?"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 221552.0,
      "end_time": 224483.0,
      "text": "There seems to be no room in the current education system"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 224484.0,
      "end_time": 227436.0,
      "text": "for the most important questions in a child's life:"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 227436.0,
      "end_time": 228724.0,
      "text": "What am I good at?"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 228724.0,
      "end_time": 230908.0,
      "text": "What do I want to do in life?"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 230908.0,
      "end_time": 233351.0,
      "text": "How do I fit into this world?"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 233352.0,
      "end_time": 235915.0,
      "text": "The system doesn't seem to care."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 235915.0,
      "end_time": 238130.0,
      "text": "There are so many greatly talented people"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 238130.0,
      "end_time": 241171.0,
      "text": "who failed in the traditional school system."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 241171.0,
      "end_time": 244747.0,
      "text": "Fortunately, they were able to overcome these failures."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 244747.0,
      "end_time": 247720.0,
      "text": "But not everyone can."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 247720.0,
      "end_time": 249206.0,
      "text": "We have no measure for how much talent,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 249206.0,
      "end_time": 253373.0,
      "text": "how much potential goes unrecognized in the current system."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 254907.0,
      "end_time": 257240.0,
      "text": "Differences in how we learn."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 258117.00000000003,
      "end_time": 260696.00000000003,
      "text": "Each of us is also different in how we learn,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 260696.00000000003,
      "end_time": 263770.0,
      "text": "in how much time we take to learn something,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 263770.0,
      "end_time": 267489.0,
      "text": "and what tools and resources work best for us."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 267489.0,
      "end_time": 270570.0,
      "text": "But the system has no room for such differences."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 270571.0,
      "end_time": 272930.0,
      "text": "So, if you're a bit slow in learning something,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 272930.0,
      "end_time": 275414.0,
      "text": "you are considered a failure,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 275414.0,
      "end_time": 279580.0,
      "text": "when all you needed was a bit more time to catch up."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 280485.0,
      "end_time": 282133.0,
      "text": "Lecturing."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 282133.0,
      "end_time": 284322.0,
      "text": "In the current system, children are lectured"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 284322.0,
      "end_time": 286420.0,
      "text": "for more than five hours a day."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 286420.0,
      "end_time": 289414.0,
      "text": "But there are a few big problems with lecturing."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 289414.0,
      "end_time": 292236.0,
      "text": "Sal Khan from Khan Academy calls lecturing"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 292237.0,
      "end_time": 295300.0,
      "text": "\"a fundamentally dehumanizing experience\"."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 295300.0,
      "end_time": 296981.0,
      "text": "\"30 kids with fingers on their lips,"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 296981.0,
      "end_time": 299796.0,
      "text": "\"not allowed to interact with each other.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 299797.0,
      "end_time": 301668.0,
      "text": "Also, in any given classroom,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 301668.0,
      "end_time": 304979.0,
      "text": "different students are at different levels of understanding."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 304979.0,
      "end_time": 306647.0,
      "text": "Now, whatever the teacher does,"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 306648.0,
      "end_time": 307964.0,
      "text": "there are bound to be students"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 307964.0,
      "end_time": 309939.0,
      "text": "who are either bored because they're ahead,"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 309939.0,
      "end_time": 312535.0,
      "text": "or confused because they're behind."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 312535.0,
      "end_time": 314682.0,
      "text": "Because of the Internet and digital media,"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 314682.0,
      "end_time": 318516.0,
      "text": "our children have at their fingertips all the information in the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 318544.0,
      "end_time": 322050.0,
      "text": "Technology has made it possible for anyone to learn anything,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 322245.0,
      "end_time": 324355.0,
      "text": "but for fear of losing control,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 324355.0,
      "end_time": 328522.0,
      "text": "the system is not leveraging these incredible resources."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 329554.0,
      "end_time": 332840.0,
      "text": "Our system of education, which evolved in the Industrial Age,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 332871.0,
      "end_time": 336107.0,
      "text": "has become outdated and ineffective."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 336107.0,
      "end_time": 338694.0,
      "text": "If we want to prepare our children for the modern world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 338694.0,
      "end_time": 342610.0,
      "text": "if we want learning to be effective and engaging,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 342610.0,
      "end_time": 344395.0,
      "text": "then there's no doubt that we need to"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 344395.0,
      "end_time": 348145.0,
      "text": "fundamentally change our system of education."
    }
  ]
}